data.description: Welcome to 206 Trenton Place. This beautiful and well maintained home is located in Lexington Plantation within the heart of Cameron. Near many shopping and dining options, the location of this home is great. This home is in a safe neighborhood that includes a clubhouse, fitness center and community pool. It has an open concept with a grand two story foyer accented by wainscoting. The kitchen looks right into the livingroom and in between is a cute coffee station. The spacious and well groomed backyard has had a new wooden fence installed and is just waiting for your next BBQ. Come see this home before it's too late!
